        <text><![CDATA[ <p> <strong>Permanent Tax Cuts for American Families Act of 2023 </strong></p> <p>This bill permanently increases the standard tax deduction for nonitemizing taxpayers. It also requires an inflation adjustment to the increased deduction amounts. </p>]]></text>
